gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 136, Wizards 128
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Wizards, 136-128. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded 32 points, six rebounds, and five assists for the Thunder, with Chet Holmgren adding 31 points, four rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied 24 points and five assists for the Wizards in the defeat. The Thunder improve to 24-11 in the regular season, while the Wizards fall to 6-30.
